data.enText: a player whose job is to stop the ball from going into his or her own team's goal

tr: the defensive position on an ice hockey or soccer or lacrosse team who stands in front of the goal and tries to prevent opposing players from scoring
the soccer or hockey player assigned to protect the goal

value.def: A goalkeeper is the player in a sports team whose job is to guard the goal.

trans: 守门员近防系统；守门员近迫武器系统；守门员近程防御武器系统
